  "texts": [
    "While the proposed taxonomy and current discussions in our paper suit a review aimed at introducing newcomers to the field, categorizing methodologies from various perspectives, such as based on implementation time perspectives-like in-processing, pre-processing, and postprocessing [30]-provides intriguing insights for researchers focusing on method development.",
    "ConclusionWe followed a systematic approach to explore the current research trends in this field.",
    "First, we examined the present method of performing systematic mapping studies followed by other scholars.",
    "Then, we proceeded to the section where we followed the rules for portraying secondary research work in a classified and informative structure.",
    "The majority of the procedures we are following in this study are based on best practices outlined by Wieringa et al. [34], Das et al."
  ]
